23 Juny
brussel mons Rousseau
i'ay receu les cheres de 14 19 & 20 cour, ie voy que tout mes assignations
sont satisfait ce qu'il m'est fort agreable, & principalement vre prompte
tude & procurant la valleur de mes quittances, pour les quelles vous est
debite ƒ 94 3 argent de change vre traitte de ƒ300 argent de courant
ne m'est pas encor presente, il sera paye avec tout d'honneur si vre grace
a d'occasion de tirer ker londres sout mesme p £400:- cela me pourins
seront agreables
accomoder, si non vos remises me accoedderont selon vre commodite. grace
a dieu de suis satisfait de S gancheret, qui m'a paye en personne & cette
ville & quand il voya que son credit, estoit caducque, il le evounia
cent mill poullies lesquelles i'ay respondu du maniere qu'il estoit
Enfin bienaise de le retirer
23 Juny
London Jan Kent & comp
conce my I writt you 19 cur & advised yotu att large the needfull about
the Spanish cloths I desire, sence haveing non from you, can not dilaye
to oxpres you my resentiment I have to see the nothrens cloathes you to
zent mee, at first their g ennevally sort deare, & bat that I can not self
one priice the 5 shillingh cloths, here not so good of forgnar the 4ƒt cloths
the 4st cloths here lire cours dozens, now there in I monst have patieuce
& tadie as the markett doth afford supposeing Iam served as eheap a5
an other, butt do finde cullours that I bid not demanded doth vex mee the
Most, my order was to you 6 march, gecording to which I should have had 8 darck
grayes as the patterne here under, and thery is butt 3 p, though dat cullour wee
want most I alsoo writ sed and send the inclosed patternes for mode cullours
beeng a drap instead where of, you send mee al ever mode cullours, so that I
finde 12 p, of which 6 is enough for a whote yeare now you hare to provide
for mee 3 packx of northrens cloathes, according to the instructions sent
you 5 may last where in N.8. and N.10 are also mode cullours, though
Must upon thered, leave out the cullour of N510 & lett me have imall
2p N. 8 yett more upon the red, and if not wel to be had, send darck
grayes instead, observing to sent mot of the darket sort as N1 „ 2, 3 in the
laid instruction, for I do not love to see cullours & goods that I can
not sell, this as mr Roosendael Saith, that you have to much to do
& there fore all things do not go as they should go, and in the meane
while when the goods are here wee are plegued to putt them of when
they are not well conditioned in cullours or in prices, soo pray M Kont
lock particulerly ofter my affairs whilst I rest
23 Juny
Amst Geert Baler Rover
IIn antwoort aende ue van 19 & 20 deser, wegens geassureerde is t wel als oock
t gene ue seght nopende de provisie, sal geirne verstant dat lameert annis costij
sal sijn aengecommen, & mijn pack sos, gelost ende herrewaerts versonden, dat pack
heeft malheureus geweest, synde met het voorgaende rotterdams convoij gelaeden
geweest in t'schep van eene eswilder die door ongeluck wiert inde pout
gestooten, soo dat het tot londen is moetten herdroeght ende opgedaen woorden
& geljck met de laeste engelse brieven nu verstaen sijnder 3 stucken lakens
daer gebleven, oversulckx soo alreede niet is verclaert, soo gelieft in plaets van 6
maer 5 spaense lakens aen te geven, beneffens 12 dosijntiens ende 1 witten balj
werdich ƒ 950::- in plaets van ƒ 1050 doch in gevalle alreede verclaert waere
geen veranderinge te doen, de negotie is hier volcoomen stil, can mijne
ardasse syde niet vercoopen, alles waght naer den uijtslagh van namen &
blijve
